result.name: Amphawa 安柏娃

reviews.text: Been a few times during lunch times! The place has been serving the food at the acceptable taste. The set lunches are hk$58 with choice of one main dish plus a drink. Only a few tables in it but the food wall hanging big photos of various dishes in stunning colors. It would be nice if the main entrance replaced with a door instead of plastic pieces where the cool air from old air con all leaking out.

delicious, nice staff. squeezy seating. yet still good to visit.

support our local diners 💪🏻 

please fix the ventilation. the cooking smell is too strong. we all smell like cooked food after the meal 😝 thanks
Set lunch is good at reasonable price and you may order BBQ sticks with set lunch. Dinner is relatively expensive.

Great authentic Thai food in a small restaurant.  Inexpensive lunch sets available.  Environment isn’t great though.  A good place for a quick lunch.

ps still can’t figure out why they always put chopsticks on the left
